    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You straighten your back, drawing in as deep a breath as you can, then lean forward as you shout, letting out a sound far far louder and more dangerous than normal.</em></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Constitution</strong> <strong>Save</strong></span></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure</strong>: Target takes [[/damage 1d6 thunder]] damage.*</p></li><li><p><strong>Success</strong>: No damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">*At Higher Levels:</strong> This spell's damage increases by 1d6 when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d6 thunder]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d6 thunder]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d6 thunder]]).</span></p>",
